pending on the different resampling rate.\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: H2dpyw5Bghv", "files": ["dom/media/mediasink/AudioSink.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "1421239eef77ff58aaf7883a366d8f97536cdfa2", "parents": ["3cb1ce131f7cab332f036cecd59e5d104c981fa8"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Alastor Wu \u003calwu@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1398139 - part2 : adjust sample's start time for chained ogg. r=jya\n\nFor chained ogg files, the new part would contain new timestamp from zero, so\nwe need to add the duration of previously decoded data to make sure the current\ntime is correct.\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: Bb1lCiKz4uQ", "files": ["dom/media/ogg/OggDemuxer.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "9fe90be81abbcc63f2c0aab66222eb867b968990", "parents": ["1421239eef77ff58aaf7883a366d8f97536cdfa2"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Alastor Wu \u003calwu@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1398139 - part3 : check current time should be increased correctly in new chained part. r=jya\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: 3ctF8SAVcs9", "files": ["dom/media/test/test_chaining.html"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "39e86cbf34d57f5478838b9b0166ba44c4f68a71", "parents": ["9fe90be81abbcc63f2c0aab66222eb867b968990"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Alastor Wu \u003calwu@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1398139 - part4 : enable test. r=jya\n\nFix the fail by patch1, so we can re-enable it.\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: It3JkvQzAdk", "files": ["dom/media/mediasource/test/mochitest.ini"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "69fec8b3a6a0dc196f2ff465259e9587182c389f", "parents": ["39e86cbf34d57f5478838b9b0166ba44c4f68a71"], "tags": []}, {"author": "ffxbld", "branch": "default", "desc": "No bug, Automated HSTS preload list update from host bld-linux64-spot-361 - a=hsts-update", "files": ["security/manager/ssl/nsSTSPreloadList.errors", "security/manager/ssl/nsSTSPreloadList.inc"], "git_node": null, "