dpi on Windows 10, r=jmaher\n\nThis started failing when migrating from Windows 8 -\u003e Windows 10. Fix is\ntracked in bug 1400357.\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: HO0AYGjVTGm", "files": ["browser/base/content/test/performance/hidpi/browser.ini"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "fed3a10c6ffc85ec56c2af4c0afc59b2e15d76f6", "parents": ["d928ad6475d220434dcd96681a4d659d8404dd32"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Andrew Halberstadt \u003cahalberstadt@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1397229 - Disable toolkit/browser/components/tooltiptext/browser_input_file_tooltips.js on Win10, r=jmaher\n\nThis started failing when migrating from Windows 8 -\u003e Windows 10. Fix is\ntracked in bug 1400368.\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: BIKAQDcJnXR", "files": ["toolkit/components/tooltiptext/tests/browser.ini"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "1c9f780c4e9c5d34d1dce011480bffd789c5ee9c", "parents": ["fed3a10c6ffc85ec56c2af4c0afc59b2e15d76f6"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Andrew Halberstadt \u003cahalberstadt@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1397229 - Schedule mochitest-browser-chrome tests on Windows 10 instead of Windows 8, r=jmaher\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: FqmgeKc1b9o", "files": ["taskcluster/ci/test/test-sets.yml", "taskcluster/ci/test/tests.yml"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "cb09c5099e519f615038109f0da3da190555775b", "parents": ["1c9f780c4e9c5d34d1dce011480bffd789c5ee9c"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Jan Odvarko \u003codvarko@gmail.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1400866 - Update Netmonitor's webpack config; r=nchevobbe\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: 4FNK3j3filG", "files": ["devtools/client/netmonitor/webpack.config.js"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "d04dd09068bb88890ab2e88da3b82c2cc24f4fa8", "parents": ["cb09c5099e519f615038109f0da3da190555775b"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Brad Werth \u003cbwerth@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1399941 Part 2: Add more aspect-rat