 in bug 1400489, to re-enable shared global for\nJSMs on mobile. r=me for trivial patch.\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: 5Kn5LFK66w8", "files": ["browser/app/profile/firefox.js", "modules/libpref/init/all.js"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "cf450ba78f02b0eb5c3f4d1476913360b6781118", "parents": ["4edef41c7f6cc02c862cadb7195e346cbb27e7ba"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Manish Goregaokar \u003cmanishsmail@gmail.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "servo: Merge #18556 - Bump cssparser to 0.21.2 (from Manishearth:cssparserup); r=emilio\n\ntry: https://treeherder.mozilla.org/#/jobs?repo=try&revision=5efe06f4fdb11e540532b57368b78defb0bd7aa9\n\nfixes https://bugzilla.mozilla.org/show_bug.cgi?id=1401016\n\nSource-Repo: https://github.com/servo/servo\nSource-Revision: 4f98a3f56a0718e6d7dbb6e360b64d5070706241", "files": ["servo/Cargo.lock", "servo/components/style/Cargo.toml"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "6beb495c45a589db8f48f289f6a11c4b3c39cf39", "parents": ["cf450ba78f02b0eb5c3f4d1476913360b6781118"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Manish Goregaokar \u003cmanishearth@gmail.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1401016 - Bump cssparser to 0.21.2; r=SimonSapin\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: 37Neluf2ETi\n", "files": ["toolkit/library/gtest/rust/Cargo.lock", "toolkit/library/rust/Cargo.lock"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "f225956e4d48c6f86a8f97f15035dec3ee88fb50", "parents": ["6beb495c45a589db8f48f289f6a11c4b3c39cf39"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Servo VCS Sync \u003cservo-vcs-sync@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "No bug - Revendor rust dependencies", "files": ["third_party/rust/cssparser/.cargo-checksum.json", "third_party/rust/cssparser/Cargo.toml", "third_party/rust/cssparser/src/nth.rs"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "8699ae18ef13b3432432f43ee67366a4b39e7b6e", "parents": ["f225956e4d48c6f86a8f97f15035dec3ee88fb50"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Markus Stange \u003cmstange@themasta.com\u003e", "