st-only\n\nThe WebDriver specification requires IPv6 addresses to be always added\nwith brackets for proxy hosts. But Firefox itself handles those without\nbrackets for both the proxy host, and the noProxy settings.\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: 9vpvXjDDuxd", "files": ["testing/marionette/session.js", "testing/marionette/test_session.js"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "64117629c89a44c6184c44dd40aaf95fbcaeb6a5", "parents": ["3ec4cc626311ecccd5cde96f20cde805c797c247"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Henrik Skupin \u003cmail@hskupin.info\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1406763 - Fix broken Assert.throws() calls for error class. r=ato, a=test-only\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: H1fw7VitAyO", "files": ["testing/marionette/test_session.js"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "503771cc0879f8a4b9a403429f35c23f9b0f9ef0", "parents": ["64117629c89a44c6184c44dd40aaf95fbcaeb6a5"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Ryan VanderMeulen \u003cryanvm@gmail.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1407437 - Unskip test_security.py. r=jmaher, a=test-only", "files": ["testing/firefox-ui/tests/puppeteer/manifest.ini"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "67a0dbdbd826ae06fe60fd242ddaab19620c69cd", "parents": ["503771cc0879f8a4b9a403429f35c23f9b0f9ef0"], "tags": []}, {"author": "JW Wang \u003cjwwang@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1402584 - Reset readyState to HAVE_NOTHING before loading next source child. See comment 18 for the root cause. r=gerald, a=ritu\n\nAlso assert readyState is HAVE_NOTHING before creating a new decoder.\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: B0QACf96AA3", "files": ["dom/html/HTMLMediaElement.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "6c786f0d59bcf548ed751bd3803441d672fde5b8", "parents": ["67a0dbdbd826ae06fe60fd242ddaab19620c69cd"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Robert Longson \u003clongsonr@gmail.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1398806 - GetCtx and GetNearestViewport should return the nearest svg or 