kupin \u003cmail@hskupin.info\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1396880 - Skip not relevant checks in test_accessibility for webdriver click. r=ato, a=test-only\n\nThe test currently performs checks which will no longer raise the expected\naccessibility exceptions if the webdriver conforming click is enabled. In\nsuch a condition those specific situations are already covered in\ntest_click.py.\n\nAs long as the legacy click has not been fully removed keep running the\nchecks but only if the webdriver click is not in use.\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: 1DbKfJYADp", "files": ["testing/marionette/harness/marionette_harness/tests/unit/test_accessibility.py"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "5ddf0b9c8ff294b1a530724379095c822f8c7b89", "parents": ["27a4dff9d4d58d784beb04c9084888d901806531"], "tags": []}], "date": 1508419400, "git_changesets": [null, null], "user": "ryanvm@gmail.com"}, "8009": {"changesets": [{"author": "Andrea Marchesini \u003camarchesini@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1404910 - WebSocket should consider the corrent top-level window principal. r=smaug, a=ritu", "files": ["dom/base/WebSocket.cpp", "dom/base/test/iframe_webSocket_sandbox.html", "dom/base/test/mochitest.ini", "dom/base/test/test_webSocket_sandbox.html"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "02b7917df086f58533fdc5fd3573e01c1ab66071", "parents": ["5ddf0b9c8ff294b1a530724379095c822f8c7b89"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Jan Henning \u003cjh+bugzilla@buttercookie.de\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1404111 - Part 0: Fix Javadoc. r=JanH, a=ritu\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: 69yqr7ybioX", "files": ["mobile/android/geckoview/src/main/java/org/mozilla/gecko/GeckoView.java"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "ed1ece91fe042cd33d9c16ca9a2dfc98a3fe6dc1", "parents": ["02b7917df086f58533fdc5fd3573e01c1ab66071"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Jan Henning \u003cjh+bugzilla@buttercookie.de\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1404111 - Part