w-Commit-ID: 98jIGHzIHlr", "files": ["mobile/android/branding/beta/res/drawable-nodpi/firstrun_welcome.png", "mobile/android/branding/nightly-old-id/res/drawable-nodpi/firstrun_welcome.png", "mobile/android/branding/nightly/res/drawable-nodpi/firstrun_welcome.png", "mobile/android/branding/official/res/drawable-nodpi/firstrun_welcome.png", "mobile/android/branding/unofficial/res/drawable-nodpi/firstrun_welcome.png"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "b1f8fcfb3260e3f35002a4ca5df8ac80e09aa828", "parents": ["4b23a41c71b8f0f229de9d3e5ee9f4bb7f0cc9a4"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Aaron Klotz \u003caklotz@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1409545 - Add the ability to query a handler provider for the expected interface for an IUnknown outparam. r=jimm, a=ritu\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: 7eZ2giTfVG1", "files": ["ipc/mscom/IHandlerProvider.h", "ipc/mscom/MainThreadHandoff.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "c2e0c41241893e8ce7844dd50064a57c97e6aa09", "parents": ["b1f8fcfb3260e3f35002a4ca5df8ac80e09aa828"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Aaron Klotz \u003caklotz@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1406822 - Implement a11y::HandlerProvider::GetEffectiveOutParamIid. r=Jamie, a=ritu\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: BKH3ooMQvN1", "files": ["accessible/ipc/win/HandlerProvider.cpp", "accessible/ipc/win/HandlerProvider.h"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "c19fd45614748b503df767817f0ad2b7a197ee31", "parents": ["c2e0c41241893e8ce7844dd50064a57c97e6aa09"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Aaron Klotz \u003caklotz@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1409541 - Replace IID_IUnknown with expected interfaces for outparams in a11y content ArrayData. r=Jamie, a=ritu\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: 4t0h8zH2hsB", "files": ["accessible/ipc/win/PlatformChild.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "745e43737c952cb24494fb844769e76a5c729c65", "parents": ["c19fd45614748b503df767817f0ad2b7a197ee31"], "tags": []}, {"author": "JW Wang \u003cjwwang@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1409649 - Shut down the decoder when MEDIA_ERR_ABORTED is received. r=gerald, a=ritu\n\nhttp://searchfox.org/mozilla-central/rev/dca019c94bf3a840ed7ff50261483410cfece24f/dom/html/HTMLMediaElement.cpp#1395-1400\n\nWe need to shut down the decoder after setting network state to EMPTY.\nOtherwise the decoder will keep loading and change ready state to HAVE_METADATA\nor greater and then fail the assertion in AssertReadyStateIsNothing().\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: FpMDVAJHTS5", "files": ["dom/html/HTMLMediaElement.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "f9d82e6c24c6039469356065d4bf27e331e12b72", "parents": ["745e43737c952cb24494fb844769e76a5c729c65"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Mike de Boer \u003cmdeboer@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1387808 - Switch to using XUL spacer elements for the zoom and edit controls' leading space in the app menu to fix auto-sizing issues. r=jaws, a=ritu\n\nWhen the locale has a slightly longer label for 'Zoom', the popup auto-sizing\ncode starts having trouble with the inline start padding of that label and doesn't\nsize the popup correctly anymore.\nWhen I change this to using a spacer element, this issue no longer occurs and the\nlabel may become as large as localizers may need, as long as it doesn't exceed\nthe max-width of a panelview - 30em, currently.\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: CHRheMqazrj", "files": ["browser/components/customizableui/content/panelUI.inc.xul", "browser/themes/osx/customizableui/panelUI.css", "browser/themes/shared/customizableui/panelUI.inc.css"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "6495434fe826662a8f606a6a28ef53e57bd46457", "parents": ["f9d82e6c24c6039469356065d4bf27e331e12b72"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Nevin Chen(:nechen) \u003ccnevinchen@gmail.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1410338 - Incorrect color for History Panel message. r=nechen, a=ritu\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: A1QmvbFt7ok", "files": ["mobile/android/app/src/main/res/layout/home_empty_panel.xml"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "1b1c2b18e426340fd414efbb81d63d8c9cc0e991", "parents": ["6495434fe826662a8f606a6a28ef53e57bd46457"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Aaron Klotz \u003caklotz@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1383131 - Fall back to ole32.dll if combase.dll is not present. r=davidb, a=ritu\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: 3plQGwqaeP9", "files": ["accessible/windows/msaa/Compatibility.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "09539becfa9a68096205fa70f7b5b8686fcc79f5", "parents": ["1b1c2b18e426340fd414efbb81d63d8c9cc0e991"], "tags": []}, {"author": "D\u00e3o Gottwald \u003cdao@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1398142 - Always specify .tab-throbber size so that pinned tabs can be positioned correctly before the session has been restored. r=jaws, a=ritu\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: 6u1jR93EMu2", "files": ["browser/themes/shared/tabs.inc.css"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "c8c16ef5be63d4803b3bbe0194f745d3ba582d2c", "parents": ["09539becfa9a68096205fa70f7b5b8686fcc79f5"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Milan Sreckovic \u003cmilan@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1387799 - Keep an extra reference. r=jrmuizel, a=ritu", "files": ["gfx/layers/ipc/CompositorBridgeChild.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "598d726067c4fa4718fcc09cdf3e5f6b9b0b6eae", "parents": ["c8c16ef5be63d4803b3bbe0194f745d3ba582d2c"], "tags": []}], "date": 1508886929, "git_changesets": [null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null], "user": "ryanvm@gmail.com"}, "8043": {"changesets": [{"author": "L10n Bumper Bot \u003crelease+l10nbumper@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "no bug - Bumping Fennec l10n changesets DONTBUILD r=release a=l10n-bump\n\nff -\u003e 7f39c7b60244\nid -\u003e f85a69ef4900\nms -\u003e aa315ffeb1ab", "files": ["mobile/locales/l10n-changesets.json"], "git_no